_sText:
Started this a while ago, made up until the 3rd stage, then just got bored of it. Came back to it a couple days ago and finished. I feel like it's pretty easy to see how much I've improved since then. Should be over a minute on auto, and I tried to add in some challenging parts since every map on gamebanana recently is a boring strafe map. Not really sure if it's possible on scroll, but I think it might be.

I'd love to hear your feedback, have fun running this!

(also I don't really know why I chose this name but it's kinda autistic)
